    "headline": "LPL Financial Hires $2.4 Billion Financial Advisory Team From U.S. Bank",
    "summary": "A five-person financial advisory team has joined  LPL Financial  from  U.S. Bank  where they oversaw $2.4 billion in client assets.  The team, which goes by HighWater Wealth and is based in San Diego, joined LPL’s brokerage and registered investment advisory channel.  While independent, HighWater Wealth organized under Quotient Advisor Partners, an LPL office of supervisory jurisdiction that helps support advisory teams setting out on their own.",
